msg: use java command from java.home, not off the path.  In some environments the vm being used is not that which is on the path.

author: dkulp
msg: Move wsdls from build/classes-tests/wsdl to build/wsdl as eclipse has a habit of wiping out any of it's "output" folders.
Add build/wsdl to the classpaths for unit and system tests as well as eclipse's classpath.  This allows all the tests to be run from eclipse. (tested all the system tests)
Make system tests and unit tests all use getResource("/wsdl/thewsdl.wsld") so they are all the same.
